OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA wet end to
OL,6,Fthe day with heavy rain or showers.
OL,7,FThis persisting throughout much of the
OL,8,Fnight before gradually clearing
OL,9,Feastwards for most by dawn. Turning
OL,10,Fchilly in the countryside with
OL,11,Fisolated fog patches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA damp morning in the east
OL,14,Fwith rain easing. Sunny spells through
OL,15,Fthe afternoon with cloud thickening
OL,16,Ffrom the west later with freshening
OL,17,Fwinds later. Feeling less mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
