OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWetter
OL,6,Fand windier on Sunday with occasional
OL,7,Fdrizzly rain, this most frequent over
OL,8,Fthe hills. Showery rain still possible
OL,9,Fon Monday. Drier and brighter on
OL,10,FTuesday. Staying mild.
